atom.val:
Given a list `is` of monotonically increasing indices into `l`, getting each index
  produces a sublist of `l`.  -/

Given a sublist `l' <+ l`, there exists an increasing list of indices `is` such that
  `l' = is.map fun i => l[i]`. -/
